title: Metal Gear OSTs - Original MG 1 & 2 for MSX
description:
Contains 4 soundtracks:
-----------------------

1. Metal Gear MSX Original Soundtrack (the real MG1 not the lame NES version)

2. Metal Gear 2: Solid Snake Original Soundtrack MSX

3. Metal Gear - Metal Gear 2 Music Collection (an album released by Konami Containing             

the best of MG 1 & 2 for MSX)

4. Metal Gear Solid Snake - RED DISC (arranged music version of MG2:Solid Snake MSX 

game)
